'''Umugwaneza Charlotte''' umwe mubakinnyi beza usanzwe ari kapiteni w'ikipe ya APR Basketball Club mu cyiciro cy'[[Umugore|abagore]]. 

== UMWIRONDORO ==
'''Umugwaneza Charlotte''' [yavutse ku ya 24 [[Ugushyingo]] 1989] mu [[Umurenge wa Gasaka|uMurenge wa Gasaka]], mu [[akarere ka Nyamagabe]] mu [[Intara y'amajyepfo|iNtara y'Amajyepfo]], '''Umugwaneza''' ni we wenyine warokotse mu [[Umuryango w’Abibumye|umuryango]] w'[[abana]] kane - [[Umwana|abakobwa]] batatu n'umuhungu [[Rimwe|umwe]]. Ababyeyi be '''Aaron Mazuru''' na '''Susan Mukagahima''' na barumuna be bose bishwe mu gihe cya [[Jenoside mu Rwanda|Jenoside]] [[Jenoside mu Rwanda|yakorewe]] [[Jenoside mu Rwanda|Abatutsi]] [[Jenoside mu Rwanda|mu]] [[Jenoside mu Rwanda|1994]] yahitanye [[Abaturage Rusange|abantu]] barenga miliyoni, '''Umugwaneza''' yarezwe na nyirasenge.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/208557</ref>

== AMASOMO YIZE ==
'''Umugwaneza Charlotte''' Yize muri rwunge rwa mashuri rwa Gasaka mu [[Akarere ka Nyamagabe|akarere]] avukamo [[Amashuli mu Rwanda|amashuri]] abanza mbere yo kwinjira muri Groupe Scholaire Notre dAme de la Paix Cyanika<ref>https://mopawa.com/groupe-scolaire-notre-dame-de-la-paix-cyanika-gsndp-application-admission-courses-contacts-fees/</ref><ref>https://www.courseseye.com/colleges-and-universities/8641-groupe-scolaire-notre-dame-de-la-paix-cyanika-gsndp.aspx</ref> nayo iherereye mu [[akarere ka Nyamagabe]] yiga mu cyiciro rugange [tronc Common O' level] kugira ngo yige bisanzwe. Ku rwego rwa masomo y'isumbuye, yinjiye muri College Saint Emmanuel de Hanika mu [[Akarere ka Nyanza|aKarere ka Nyanza]] aho yize ibaruramari arangiza muri 2009. Mu [[umwaka]] wa 2010, yinjiye muri [[Kaminuza y'Abadiventisti bo muri Afurika yo Hagati (AUCA)|kaminuza]] [[Kaminuza y'Abadiventisti bo muri Afurika yo Hagati (AUCA)|ya Lay]] [[Kaminuza y'Abadiventisti bo muri Afurika yo Hagati (AUCA)|Adventiste]] [[Kaminuza y'Abadiventisti bo muri Afurika yo Hagati (AUCA)|ya Kigali]] [[Kaminuza y'Abadiventisti bo muri Afurika yo Hagati (AUCA)|(INILAK)]] akurikirana impamyabumenyi yi cyijiro cya mbere mu icungamari maze arangiza muri 2014. Nyuma yo kurangiza, '''Umugwaneza''' yakoranye namasosiyete menshi arimo [https://www.mtn.co.rw/ MTN Rwanda] nkumucungamari. <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/208557</ref>Umugwaneza, ufite uburebure bwa 1.95mh n'uburemere bw'ibiro  80, akaba ari umwe mu bakinnyi bakina hagati basketball y'abagore bo mu [[Rwanda]] neza.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/208557</ref>

== UBUZIMA BWITE ==
'''Umugwaneza Charlotte'''  ari mu bihumbi by’[[abana]] basigaye badafite ababyeyi kandi batagira aho baba kubera [[Jenoside mu Rwanda|jenocide]] [[Jenoside mu Rwanda|yakorewe]] [[Jenoside mu Rwanda|abatutsi]] [[Jenoside mu Rwanda|mu 1994]], bivuze ko atigeze agira amahirwe yo kubona urukundo n'ubwuzu bw'ababyeyi be. Nyuma y'urupfu rw'ababyeyi be na barumuna be,narenzwe na masenge,'''Immaculee Mukamusonera'''.  Mvugishije ukuri ubwana bwanjye cyari igihe kitoroshye. kuba narabuze umuryango wanjye nkiri muto cyane, nahatiwe gufata ibyo nahawe byose kandi ngomba kwiga byinshi nkiri muto, '''Umugwaneza''' agira ati: “Umuryango wa masenge ni umuryango wegamiye ku idini nahawe uburere no gusenga nyamara nkiri muto nakundaga gukina umupira ariko masenge abyanga. nabwiye masenge kumugaragaro andeke kurikize ibyo nkunda kuva nkiri muto, kubwamahirwe, yanteze amatwi arabyemera. Kuva uwo munsi, natangiye gukina umupira ntatinya ingaruka.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/208557</ref><ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/71490/umugwaneza-charlotte-nyuma-yo-kwitabira-imikino-ya-zone-5-ya-71490.html</ref>

== Umwuga ==

=== Umupira w'amaboko ===
'''Umugwaneza Charlotte''' Nari umukinnyi w'ingenzi muri College Saint Emmanuel de Hanika.  Urebye uburebure bwanjye nogukunda siporo, mwarimu wimikino yacu yangiriye inama yo kugerageza basketball, anyemeza ko mfite imico yo kuzaba umukinnyi mwiza wa basketball kandi niko nahisemo gukina basketball, Yanyigishije iby'ibanze, uburyo bwo kwiruka n'umupira mpita mbimenya vuba. Nyuma y'ibyumweru bike, niswe izina mu ikipe y'[[ishuri]]. Mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2009, yatoranijwe kuba mu ikipe ya Basketball y'[[Umugore|abagore]] ya [[akarere ka Nyanza]] yitabiriye “Imiyoborere Cup Cup” - iyi kipe yageze ku mukino wa nyuma w'[[igihugu]] ariko itsindwa na [[Akarere ka Nyarugenge|Nyarugenge]]. Muri iryo rushanwa niho '''Charles Mushumba''', umutoza mukuru wa [[IPRC Huye|IPRC-Amajyepfo]], icyo gihe akaba yaratozaga ikipe y’[[Umugore|abagore]] yahoze ari [[Kaminuza nkuru y’u Rwanda|kaminuza]] [[Kaminuza nkuru y’u Rwanda|nkuru y’u]] [[Kaminuza nkuru y’u Rwanda|Rwanda]] [[Kaminuza y'u Rwanda|(NUR),]] yaramubonye maze amwemeza ko yinjira mu ikipe ye, ari yo yarushanwaga mu [[Umugore|bagore]] b’[[igihugu]]. Yaje kandi kuganira  na masenge maze ntangira kuva i [[Akarere ka Nyamagabe|Nyamagabe]] kugera [[Akarere ka Huye|Huye]] buri munsi kugira ngo nitoze, amezi atatu.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/208557</ref><ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/202103310232.html</ref><ref>https://www.fiba.basketball/womensafrobasket/2019/qualifiers/player/Charlotte-Umugwaneza#tab=stats,career_stats</ref><ref>https://basketball.afrobasket.com/player/Charlotte-Umugwaneza/Rwanda/APR-BBC-Kigali/281280?Women=1</ref>

=== Kubaka umwuga ===
'''Umugwaneza Charlotte''' ubwo yitabiraga urishannya rya Zone V yabereye i Kampala yashimishije umutoza mukuru wa APR, '''Charles Mbazumutima'''.Inyungu za APR zahuriranye n’uko '''Umugwaneza''' yimukiye i [[Kigali]] aho yagombaga gutangira [[Amashuri Makuru|amashuri]] ya [[Kaminuza y'Abadiventisti bo muri Afurika yo Hagati (AUCA)|kaminuza]] muri [[Kaminuza y'Abadiventisti bo muri Afurika yo Hagati (AUCA)|INILAK]], bityo akajya mu ikipe y'igisirikare mu 2010.  Ati: Byari bigoye kubona umwanya wo gukina muri APR icyo gihe kuko bari bafite abakinnyi benshi beza kandi b'inararibonye b'abanyamahanga kandi numvaga shaka gukina cyane, ariko umutoza yakomeje kuntera inkunga kandi namaze hafi [[umwaka]] ntinjiye mu ikipe yambere. ikipe kugeza 2011 ubwo club yatangiraga gukoresha abakinnyi ba banyarwanda. iyi ikipe nayibereye kapiteni, nyobora iyi kipe mu ibikombe bitandatu bya shampiyona isanzwe, ibikombe bitandatu bya playoff, bituma iba ikipe yatsinze cyane, yagizwe umukinnyi mwiza wo hagati w[[umwaka]]. '''Umugwaneza''' Hamwe na APR, '''Umugwaneza''' yanitabiriye amarushanwa ya [[Afurika|Afrika]] Zone V Club buri [[Umwaka|mwaka]], abura gusa 2016.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/208557</ref><ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/71490/umugwaneza-charlotte-nyuma-yo-kwitabira-imikino-ya-zone-5-ya-71490.html</ref><ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/202103310232.html</ref><ref>https://www.fiba.basketball/womensafrobasket/2019/qualifiers/player/Charlotte-Umugwaneza#tab=stats,career_stats</ref><ref>https://basketball.afrobasket.com/player/Charlotte-Umugwaneza/Rwanda/APR-BBC-Kigali/281280?Women=1</ref>

=== Ibyo ashaka kugeraho ===
'''Umugwaneza Charlotte''' Agira ati: Nizera ko basketball yampinduye uwo ndiwe uyu munsi kandi sinkeka ko nzareka gukina vuba, kandi ko igihe nzajya  mu kiruhuko cy'izabukuru, nizera ko nzakomeza umwuga wo gutoza cyangwa umusifuzi.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/208557</ref><ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/71490/umugwaneza-charlotte-nyuma-yo-kwitabira-imikino-ya-zone-5-ya-71490.html</ref>

=== Abo ashimira ===
'''Umugwaneza Charlotte''' Mbere na mbere, ndashimira [[Imana]] kuba ndi muzima kandi ikampa impano-Ndashimira kandi masenge n'umuryango we, kuba barujuje icyuho cy'ababyeyi banjye mu buzima bwanjye, umutoza '''Musumba''', wambonye bwa mbere kandi ndashimira  abo dukorana muri APR, akaba ari umuryango wanjye wa [[kabiri]].<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/208557</ref><ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/71490/umugwaneza-charlotte-nyuma-yo-kwitabira-imikino-ya-zone-5-ya-71490.html</ref>

